HEADWORD: Octennial
<hw>Oc*ten"ni*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>octennium</ets> a period of eight years; <ets>octo</ets> eight +
<ets>annus</ets> year.]</ety> <def>Happening every eighth year; also,
lasting a period of eight years.</def> <au>Johnson.</au> --
<wordforms><wf>Oc*ten"ni*al*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

